data.description: If you're dreaming of a full time residence on the coast, or vacation house near the beach, you're in luck! This home is ready for your magic touch. This home sits on just under an acre, awaiting your creative vision. Boasting 1,930 sq feet of living space, there is plenty of room to sprawl out. As you arrive at the home you are welcomed by a pull through driveway, allowing for easy access to your home. As you enter the home you will be entranced by the vaulted ceilings and ample natural light entering the living space. This beautiful beach home is located a short distance to the Sunset Beach entrance and near the Astoria Golf and Country Club. Just a short distance to shopping centers in Warrenton and a short drive to all Seaside has to offer. If you have dogs or enjoy long walks, the Cullaby Lake Trail head is just a short distance from your front door and is a magical walk to take every day. This property is a must see! Schedule your showing today.
